page.title: 15HOME + FAMILY IN CARLISLE<2>
page.content: I live at 66 Moorhouse Road and our nextdoor neighbour is called Mrs. Wil- son.I have got a budgie called Louie but she stays at my grandma's house.We used to have a goldfish called George but he died.Before I was born my mam and dad used to live at Kendal,but then they had to move because of my dad's job.I have got two uncles and aunties.My Auntie Marjorie died,so my Uncle Alan got married again to Carolyn.She has got two children called Roger and Jane.Roger is 8 or 9 and Jane will be 6 on June 20th.My Uncle Alan has got two girls called Judith and Brenda.Judith is 15 and Brenda is 14 and Carolyn is having another baby in the Autumn.
